The lyrics are by Lawrence Schoen, and the accompanying music is by Rich Yampell.

This is directed at one person. When speaking to multiple people, say {peqIm!:sen:nolink} instead.

An appropriate reply to this is {nuqneH:excl} "What do you want?"

